Package: shinyMLLab
Title: Shiny ML & Forecasting Lab
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Malik", "Hebbat", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A pure R Shiny application for end-to-end predictive modeling.
    Upload structured or unstructured data at any cadence (daily, weekly,
    monthly, quarterly, yearly), choose from a curated registry of regression,
    classification, count, proportion, and time-series models, tune
    hyperparameters in the UI, run forecasts over configurable horizons, and
    persist every run to SQLite for comparison. Python interop via reticulate
    is optional and used only for LightGBM, CatBoost, and Keras MLP wrappers.
